name: Amanda L
text: Friendly staff and quick service at this location. I wish the nutrition information was easier to find and the salad information was a little more clear cut. They have a variety of items here, plenty to choose from and always tastes fresh.

name: Jason Gordienko
text: Really enjoyed my sandwich here. Became a go to lunch spot when I was working in this town. Great selection, service and taste

name: Larry Blake
text: Decent food. Kinda wish that they filled the sub roll more but it's a good product.

name: Jason Henriksen
text: Best D'Angelos around. Great staff and excellent food. Love this place. The #9 is where it's at!!!

name: Kay Garber
text: I will Never ever get delivery again! I ordered At 12:15 and at 1:35 still no food! They called about the address and I told Them what it was and still nothing! At this point by the time I eat, my break will be over! Horrible delivery service

text: ordered avacado pecan salade.  Got home.   no avacodo. no pecans in my salade.  Don.t think I.ll go back.  Very disappointed.

text: Surprisingly this is a great spot for a sandwich. There is a lot of value in their pricing. I've enjoyed their steak bomb on many occasions. You really can't go wrong with this place.
